title: My Random Greek Story
story: Once a group of old men bought my lunch for me in a taverna because they felt sorry for me sitting alone. I went to say thankyou and ended up sitting and having drinks with them. I ended up getting trashed with a group of orthodox priests.

title: My random Lucky Landing
story: When I was 9 I rode down a hill and crashed into a tree but of getting hurt I rolled up the tree trunk and flew across the pavement and landed safely.
